76561197982104989,Recommended,293780,31195831,Posted: 17 April,all,Mountainsides,"Should you buy this game?Yes.Crawl is a arcade throw back of yester year (even has a cabinet display option) in which you and up to three friends (or AI if you don't have any friends) face off in local multiplayer in seeing who can hit level 10  by slaying monsters and buying new equipment first to face off against the boss to gain freedom!.. With the other players attempting to murder you and wear your flesh as a suit so they can attempt the same.In between the levels players have the chance to upgrade their monsters by evolving them into such things as Beholders or Demons at the every end of each monster tree (with more being unlocked after each successful game).Having played a few games myself I would advise against buying this if you just want a single player game, it's still fun against the AI but the real enjoyment is watching the light of your friendships fade as you rob them of their hard fought victory and win the game yourself, well that's the real enjoyment for me at least (#notsorryChris)."
