76561198011244448,Recommended,293780,20199090,"Posted: 1 January, 2016",all,Legenditals,"Crawl is an awesome multiplayer (local) game in which you, your friends and AI will control up to 3 ghosts. The players will be competing for gold and experience while traversing a dungeon. One player will spawn as the hero, and the remaining players will start as ghosts. The currently alive player will move from room to room, coming across pentagrams in most rooms. The ghosts can activate these to summon one of 3 monsters chosen in a kit at the start of the game.Should a ghost deal the killing blow on the player, they spawn as the hero and must continue the dungeon! Each floor has a shop and boss ring the player can interact with, as well as other wishing wells and a few other entitys to work with.The combat is fun, there's plenty of weapons the store offers, plenty of artifacts to modify the character, as well as spells to get from the shop.Pros:A fun (currently local) fighting game for friends to challenge each other in.Plenty of weapons to choose from, a good bit of item variation.Lots of unlocks to encourage replayability.Challenging bosses that force the ghost/players to work together to kill the hero/playerMore content to come!The combat is solid and fun.Nice design for a minimalist/pixel game.Cons:While maps are randomly generated, there isn't any difference in backgrounds or themes at this time of reviewThe sound is very harsh and not appeasing at all."
