,Recommended,293780,21218274,"Posted: 14 February, 2016",all,ZeuroMaker,"For the unacquainted... 'Crawl' is a dungeon crawler with fluid pixel gameplay and mechanics. It, in its current build, it is a 4 player local multiplayer game where the friends you play with are the monsters, bosses and environmental hazards you must overcome. One player plays as the human, whilst the rest of the players take control of the ghosts of comrades that were slain by the human. If a ghost manages to kill the human, that player gains humanity and takes the place of that human. All players must fight amongst each other for this humanity, reach level 10 and kill the boss (of which, each player takes control of a section of the boss). As the human improves, the ghosts/monsters evolve stronger too. This chaotic and entertaining Indie game has brilliant potential, updates and adds new content quite often.If you ever see this game on sale and have at least one local friend also possessing a mouse and a keyboard, I urge you to buy this game and support this games development. It is a game that would be enjoyable to a wide range of individuals regardless.When online eventually comes to Crawl, It instantly becomes a must buy hands down.Give the game a chance. It is constantly improving.A purchase that you will not regret."
