,Recommended,293780,11598975,"Posted: 8 August, 2014",all,Inconsistent,"Crawl is an amazing Dungeon crawler type game. One player controls The Hero and the other players play as Ghosts. The Ghosts have to possess traps and become monsters to try and kill The Hero. Whoever lands the final blow to The Hero becomes The Hero. There is also currency in the game, You can get blood by hurting The Hero as a Ghost and you get gold by finding chests. While exploring you can find a blacksmith where you can buy better swords, spells and you can kneel down to an idol that takes all of your blood and makes it gold. That was a basic rundown of Crawl. Before you buy it though, it is only local co-op as of today but the devs said that online is a possibility. I recommend this to everybody who likes a fun multiplayer experience."
