,Recommended,293780,12183574,"Posted: 21 September, 2014",all,Kaiju,"Crawl is an amazing and very fun dungeon crawler. It can be played up to four players, one person being the hero, and the other three being ghosts. The ghosts try to kill the hero by taking over objects or using a demon circle to summon a monster to fight the hero with. If one of the ghosts kill the hero, the ghost that got the killing blow will become the new hero. At the end of every floor the ghosts will get points every time a hero leveled up, and they get to use the points to evolve their monsters. While you're the hero; you try to get to level 10 so you can open a portal to the final boss. If you kill the boss (Which the ghosts will control) you win. If not, you'll be kicked out of the portal and have a small amount of health left. If the boss isn't beaten after three tries its game over and the ghosts win. I absolutely love this game and can’t wait for the finish product."
