,Recommended,293780,29130352,Posted: 8 January,all,Coco_the_Dog_arf,"Really great local multiplayer party game. Hack and slash, roguelike, action rpg with magic abilities and all the fixings! The great hook with this game is that you and your friends play AGAINST each other.Gameplay:This game is usually played with four players, and if you're short on players you can use bots instead. One character can be the ""hero"" at a time, while the others play as disembodied ghosts whose objective is to strike a killing blow on the ""hero."" Once a ghost accomplishes this, they then become the ""hero."" Ghost players can possess traps, objects, and summon playable monsters in an effort to kill the hero. With every creature the hero kills, that player receives experience and can level up. Once a player reaches level 10, they can go through a portal and fight the boss, and if successful, win the match.After every playthrough you unlock more traps, monsters, and bosses.Verdict:Great party game to play together with friends on the couch, and a great way to end friendships :)"
