,Recommended,293780,31848771,Posted: 19 May,all,Rìventhief,"Crawl is one of the most enjoyable competitve local multiplayer experiences out there. With it's frantic mechanic of the hero getting swarmed by monsters the other players control in hopes they will slay said hero and regain their own humanity. Constant fighting in every single room, while traps are activated at the ghosts' command. Tables and chairs are thrown around the room by the ghosts, allowing them to soften the hero down if they don't expect it and dodge. There's no time to wait around as the hero, not even at the shop as the ghosts will begin collecting slimes by gathering up spirits and will ambush the hero at any given time. Finally, once a hero have reached the requirements to face the boss and get out of this enternal torment, the hero will face the ghosts as the ghosts control everything the boss has in order to kill the hero and prevent him from escaping with the valued humanity.I would greatly recommed this game even if you don't have people around to play as the bots in the game are quite skilled and will mess you up if you are not focused, I'm looking forward to what this game has in store in the future."
